        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Ok, this may sound like nitpicking, but it’s so easy to fix that I decided to report it.<br>
Under close inspection, the HDR skyboxes look very pixelated, thanks to a bug within the Source Engine.<br>
<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/original/3X/c/8/c87ace2ba7505e92235398a1ac849986d0b9df2c.jpeg" data-download-href="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/c87ace2ba7505e92235398a1ac849986d0b9df2c" title=""><img src="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/8/c87ace2ba7505e92235398a1ac849986d0b9df2c_2_690x431.jpeg" alt="" data-base62-sha1="sBwBpglUGFXH48sw8ecVna0uJ9W" width="690" height="431" srcset="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/8/c87ace2ba7505e92235398a1ac849986d0b9df2c_2_690x431.jpeg, https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/8/c87ace2ba7505e92235398a1ac849986d0b9df2c_2_1035x646.jpeg 1.5x, https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/8/c87ace2ba7505e92235398a1ac849986d0b9df2c_2_1380x862.jpeg 2x" data-small-upload="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/c/8/c87ace2ba7505e92235398a1ac849986d0b9df2c_2_10x10.png"><div class="meta"><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#far-image"></use></svg><span class="filename"></span><span class="informations">1440×900 202 KB</span><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#discourse-expand"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>
<span class="bbcode-b">Fixing:</span><br>
<img src="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/original/3X/8/9/8937cee37625a2f287c9edc08a42d9c5d6e92c3e.png" alt="" data-base62-sha1="jzSYSlj4yei53mv4RHb1x88ds3Y" width="514" height="387"><br>
Just check the “Point Sample” flag and save the file. It seems that the engine belives it’s “true” when it’s “false” and vice-versa.<br>
Fixed sky:<br>
<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/original/3X/0/9/092621625ffa6dd687be3233079b0255ec35f958.jpeg" data-download-href="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/092621625ffa6dd687be3233079b0255ec35f958" title=""><img src="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/0/9/092621625ffa6dd687be3233079b0255ec35f958_2_689x448.jpeg" alt="" data-base62-sha1="1iVZsnOFADoIK1Ae2fPQVHeLQy4" width="689" height="448" srcset="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/0/9/092621625ffa6dd687be3233079b0255ec35f958_2_689x448.jpeg, https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/0/9/092621625ffa6dd687be3233079b0255ec35f958_2_1033x672.jpeg 1.5x, https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/original/3X/0/9/092621625ffa6dd687be3233079b0255ec35f958.jpeg 2x" data-small-upload="https://leakfree.org/uploads/default/optimized/3X/0/9/092621625ffa6dd687be3233079b0255ec35f958_2_10x10.png"><div class="meta"><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#far-image"></use></svg><span class="filename"></span><span class="informations">1374×894 174 KB</span><svg class="fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#discourse-expand"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>
Also feel free to check <a href="https://spockjedi.webs.com/HDR%20TUTORIAL.html" data-bbcode="true" rel="nofollow noopener">my article.</a> There are some tips on how to properly compile HDR skyboxes there.<br>
And congratulations for the awesome mod! I can’t wait to play Xen.  <img src="https://leakfree.org/images/emoji/twitter/smiley.png?v=9" title=":smiley:" class="emoji" alt=":smiley:"></p>
